txt.en: You have discovered Galdir's Dell, a once beautiful field in Lossarnach, now scorched earth and filled with Haradrim.
You have discovered Ost Norhír, a small Orc encampment within the ruins of a small Gondorian village in Lossarnach.
You have discovered the Harlond, the port city outside of the Rammas Echor, now captured by Orc forces.
You have discovered Harlanc, a Haradrim camp within the ruins of Southern Ithilien.
Scout enemy encampments scattered throughout Eastern Gondor.
Scout enemy encampments scattered throughout Eastern Gondor.
You have discovered TBD, a former Gondorian port village in Upper Lebennin, now controlled by Haradrim.
You have discovered Aegollant, a small Haradrim encampment in Lossarnach.
You have discovered Lân Mefam, a large Haradrim encampment in South Ithilien on the road to Harad.
You have discovered Barad Nemorn, a hidden Orc encampment on the banks of the Morgulduin in Southern Ithilien.
